OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FWhen Emma Harrison went on a school
OL,7,Ftrip to Thornbridge Hall, her life was
OL,8,Fabout as far removed from the
OL,9,Fmansion's faded luxury as it is
OL,10,Fpossible to imagine.
OL,12,FWith 100 acres of its own parkland,
OL,13,Fthe vast 12th century stately home
OL,14,Fhad, over its 800-year history,
OL,15,Fvariously housed wealthy linen
OL,16,Fexporters, lawyers and the creator of
OL,17,FPinewood Studios.
