OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FIt is not quite a rags-to-riches
OL,7,Fstory, but remarkable nonetheless.
OL,9,FHaving left school after
OL,10,Funderachieving at A-level, Harrison
OL,11,Ftook a job with the Health and Safety
OL,12,FExecutive doing basic engineering
OL,13,Fwork. An engineering course led to a
OL,14,Fdegree and a job with British Steel.
OL,16,FBut when her father started a small
OL,17,Fbusiness retraining unemployed steel
OL,18,Fworkers, Harrison left to join him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
