OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FSuccess was rapid and what was a
OL,7,F#100,000 business later boomed. After
OL,8,Fbeing rebranded as Action 4 Employment
OL,9,F(A4E) it ended up with a turnover of
OL,10,Fmore than #230 million and more than
OL,11,F3,000 staff.
OL,13,FMore than 20 years after that first
OL,14,Fvisit to Thornbridge, Harrison, who
OL,15,Fwas once named on the Sunday Times
OL,16,FRich List, was with her husband on
OL,17,Fholiday when she revived the idea of
OL,18,Fowning a large house to share with
OL,19,Ffriends and family.
OL,21,FA visit to an estate agent followed.
