OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FHarrison said: "I told them 'I'm
OL,7,Flooking for a really really big
OL,8,Fhouse'. Someone there said, 'how big?'
OL,9,Fand I said 'sort of Chatsworth, but
OL,10,Fperhaps not as big as Chatsworth'.
OL,12,F"He said, 'there's only one house
OL,13,Fround here that's that big' and I
OL,14,Fsaid, 'where's that?' and he said,
OL,15,F'Thornbridge'.
OL,17,F"I'd not heard that word since I was
OL,18,F15."
