OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FHaving bought the estate, Emma and Jim
OL,7,FHarrison set about a #20 million
OL,8,Frestoration.
OL,10,F"When we first moved in, we didn't
OL,11,Fhave ceiling, we had no floors, but it
OL,12,Flooks alright now," Harrison says.
OL,14,FThat is something of an
OL,15,Funderstatement. The home now boasts 20
OL,16,Fbedrooms, 42 toilets as well as its
OL,17,Fvery own underground nightclub and a
OL,18,Fswimming pool. No surprise that it was
OL,19,Fonce branded "Britain's quirkiest
OL,20,Fstately home".
