OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FAmong its idiosyncratic interior
OL,7,Fdesign touches are lights made from
OL,8,Frecycled parts of an old pipe organ. A
OL,9,FRenaissance style portrait of Harrison
OL,10,Fhangs on one wall. There is also a
OL,11,Fsecret tunnel which takes people from
OL,12,Fone side of the estate to the other.
OL,14,FIt is home to 26 people, including
OL,15,Ffriends of the Harrisons.
