OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FEmma Harrison said: "I always thought
OL,7,FI wanted to live with my family and
OL,8,Ffriends in a really, really big space
OL,9,Fso that if anything goes wrong you've
OL,10,Falready got that support system around
OL,11,Fyou."
OL,13,FBut the estate is also open to
OL,14,Fvisitors.
OL,16,FUnlike other historic country houses,
OL,17,Fhowever, the rules are relaxed.
