OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FHarrison says: "Some very formal
OL,7,Fplaces have been to visit us and have
OL,8,Fsaid 'Wait a minute, where's all your
OL,9,Fropes, where's your room guard? Room
OL,10,Fguard! What are they about?
OL,12,F"When you come to Thornbridge you can
OL,13,Ftour the house and the tour is
OL,14,Fabsolutely bonkers. It will involve
OL,15,Fyour dogs getting on the sofas... no
OL,16,Fareas are beyond you, (you'll get)
OL,17,Fsome very funny stories as well as
OL,18,Fsome important history."
