OL,3,C'I went on a school trip to a stately
OL,4,Chome and ended up buying it'
OL,6,FHarrison hopes her unconventional
OL,7,Fstewardship of the 900-year-old
OL,8,Fproperty will rub off on others, with
OL,9,Fattitudes to the country's heritage
OL,10,Fhomes becoming less stuffy.
OL,12,FShe says: "I'd like stately homes to
OL,13,Fbecome much more chilled out. Let's
OL,14,Flose the posh stuff, because it puts
OL,15,Fpeople off. Let's throw the doors open
OL,16,Fand let's make people really comfy. My
OL,17,Ffinal gift to the nation - I've given
OL,18,Fmost of my wealth away already, by the
OL,19,Fway - will be to give them this house
OL,20,Fand everything else, and that's magic
OL,21,Ffor me."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
